data.description: 4Bd 2.5Bath Home in the pictures Canyon Hills Cottonwood Community. Home size is 2,116sq-ft and has been recently painted and upgraded flooring throughout the home. Open floor plan with a large kitchen, half bath downstairs and laundry is conveniently located upstairs with cabinets and sink. Back Yard is easy to maintain with artificial grass and has a black wall and a large patio with two fans that will keep cool and great for entertainment. Great neighborhood and lots of activities to keep the kids engaged with parks, walking trails, pool area. Don't miss-out, come and see this beautiful home, move-in ready.
